The paper deals with the problem of object manipulation for grasping in robotics, which falls under the category of Robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves image processing and machine learning techniques such as regression, optimization, and deep reinforcement learning, which are commonly used in Computer Vision (cs.CV), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with the control and decision-making aspects of the robot, which falls under the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY).
